---
title: Chicken & Corn Baked Quesadillas with Coriander Yoghurt
description: Baked quesadillas are our favourite type of quesadillas. Not only do you get the cheesy goodness and tasty Mexican filling, everything cooks all at once, meaning dinner is minimal fuss and maximum flavour! With extra veggies for goodness, and a creamy coriander yoghurt, these will quickly become your new favourite too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5be2439430006c495051e8c2-55e50066.jpg
